Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 14:09:09 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 05/10] add shell commands, make shell fullscreen, add
 show/hide terminal button

---
 index.html | 15 ++++++----
 scripts.js | 84 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 styles.css | 41 +++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 3 files changed, 133 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

